:: First indecation that something is wrong {"position":"1600,200","size":"200,200"}
Scraprat pushes Victor's head into the gamma closet, only for a moment. This causes Victor to convulse and lose consciousness almost immediately. The only reason he doesn't die is because it was a short duration of exposure.
[[What have i done .JPG]]


:: Get acepted in tribe {"position":"6525,2925","size":"200,200"}
Comet curses and says that they will have to survive with that thing around for several hours while they wait for the gamma storm to pass. Red offers some treatment to Scraprat's ruined eye and finally wraps a bandage around his head, apologizing that there isn't anything better.
[[Must work more on this one ]]


:: Gets found out {"position":"2550,200","size":"200,200"}
As Scraprat is holding Victor's head inside of the gamma closet, a woman walks in and asks about the noise. She sees Scraprat killing Victor and immediately takes out her gun in a panic.
[[ScrapRat gets gankd]]


:: Gets help {"position":"2575,425","size":"200,200"}
Woman almost immediately arrives and asks what happened. Player is given dialogue options that only affect trust levels. But he claims it was an accident of Victor.
[[found out wat can be done]]


:: Gets split up and devided with other peaple {"position":"1100,200","size":"200,200"}
Victor is passively aggressive with Scraprat, not liking his Vox origins. He makes hostile jokes, pokes fun at him, and is sometimes just outright insulting.
[[ScrapRat angry]]


:: Gives gun {"position":"7675,2050","size":"200,100"}
Comet crawls closer to him, picks up the gun, and offers it to him, saying that he knows what he should do.
[[Kill my self?]]


:: Inspection {"position":"5775,3000","size":"200,200"}
Comet asks Red if she thinks there is anything they can do. Red explains that she knows very little of the alien, and would probably need to inspect Scraprat personally to see if she can find out more. The voice in his head then freaks out, ordering him not to let her near, or it will kill him and her. Scraprat gets a terrible migraine.
[[Dhi check]]


:: Kill my self? {"position":"7950,1975","size":"100,100"}
