[[Kill's himself sad]]


:: Kill's himself sad {"position":"7950,2100","size":"200,100"}
Scraprat nods slowly, and takes the gun from Comet. He takes a moment, then says thank you, and shoots himself in the head.


:: Low trust {"position":"4475,675","size":"200,200"}
Comet does not trust him enough and turns down his request to go back. She reasons that it is not only a waste of time, but the upcoming plasma storm would make them stuck at the other sector.


:: Majer clue {"position":"4600,1025","size":"200,200"}
