:: Self introspection {"position":"3875,750","size":"200,200"}
Scraprat tries to chase the voice out and desperately tries to figure out what had changed. He then realizes there is a gap in his memory before Mac called for him. He concludes that something must have happened there, and something is terribly wrong with him.
