:: The fear is real {"position":"6450,3200","size":"200,200"}
Comet then voices her concern that other have become infected without their knowledge. Mac then suggests that it may be worth it to try and reactivate some of the higher-grade scanners in the mad bays to get more info on the alien without getting too close. The problem is that he isn't sure how they would go about doing that.
[[ScrapRat fix med stuff]]


:: The realisation of being taken over {"position":"5125,2125","size":"200,200"}
Scraprat realizes what is happening to him and is told by the voice in his head that it is only making him better and stronger. He will be more happy if he embraces it. He will still be aware, but he will be changed for the better.
[[choice of telling the others]]


:: To kill or not to kill {"position":"7400,1900","size":"100,200"}
The alien is elated and the voice in Scraprat's head praises him for his work, urging him to finish the job and kill Comet.
