:: Trust check fail {"position":"5575,2725","size":"200,200"}
The group does not trust him and become very concerned. Red voices her concern that if it infected Scraprat, it could infect more people. She goes down a line of reasoning that it may be why the whole facility was abandoned despite its use. Comet then decides it would be better to kill Scraprat before more people die.
[[RUN]]


:: Trust check succeed {"position":"5525,3025","size":"200,200"}
The group has begun to trust and like Scraprat more. They become very concerned, Red theorizes what risks the alien poses to others, but the group decides that it is worth it to see if they can help him in some way. Comet says bluntly that it would probably be smarter to kill Scraprat right now, but admits that she would rather not.
[[Inspection]]


